                  </hi>. I keep the public-house. No man came into my house with a hat—I found this hat about the middle of the court.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went up the court to go to the public-house—there were two or three men at the corner of the court.</p>
